ed%20ClassPass%20for%20clubbing%2C%20was%20a%20subscription%20service%20for%20local%20clubs.%20The%20next%20idea%20was%20a%20platform%20to%20find%20the%20best%20doctor%20for%20specific%20needs%2C%20inspired%20by%20Guo's%20own%20experience%20after%20breaking%20her%20jaw%20in%20an%20electric%20skateboard%20accident.%20With%20that%20idea%2C%20they%20applied%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-y-combinator-new-headquarters-office-san-francisco-dogpatch-photos-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartup%20accelerator%20Y%20Combinator%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20summer%202016%20batch.%20But%2C%20midway%20through%20the%20program%2C%20they%20pivoted%20again%2C%20this%20time%20to%20what%20would%20eventually%20become%20Scale%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lucy%20Guo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7e25543b5e59d16b4889b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELucy%20Guo%2C%20CEO%20of%20Passes%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Scale%20AI.%3Cp%3ELucy%20Guo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20Scale%20AI%20came%20from%20a%20suggestion%20by%20one%20of%20their%20YC%20roommates%2C%20who%20proposed%20creating%20an%20%26quot%3BAPI%20for%20humans.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20said%20that%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20that%20is%20so%20controversial%2C%26quot%3B%20Guo%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20brilliant%20idea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuo%20and%20Wang%20then%20developed%20a%20product%20to%20connect%20customers%20with%20contractors%20to%20do%20manual%20and%20time-consuming%20tasks.%20They%20initially%20focused%20on%20outsourced%20phone%20calls%20but%20quickly%20narrowed%20their%20focus%20to%20data%20labeling%20and%20quality%20control%20for%20autonomous%20vehicles%2C%20an%20emerging%20sector%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCruise%20became%20one%20of%20our%20first%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Guo%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20self-driving%20cars.%26quot%3B%20Since%20then%2C%20Scale%20AI%20has%20quickly%20grown%2C%20becoming%20a%20dominant%20force%20in%20the%20data%20labeling%20industry.%20It%20raised%20%241.6%20billion%20in%20total%20funding%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook%2C%20and%20was%20recently%20valued%20at%20%2413.8%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuo%20left%20the%20startup%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BThe%20itch%20to%20build%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Scale%20AI%2C%20Guo%20decided%20to%20apply%20her%20learnings%20to%20a%20new%20entrepreneurial%20opportunity%3A%20investing.%20Accel%2C%20one%20of%20Scale%20AI's%20investors%2C%20provided%20Guo%20with%20scout%20money%20to%20invest%20in%20startups.%20Her%20initial%20success%20led%20her%20to%20establish%20her%20own%20venture%20fund%2C%20Backend%20Capital%2C%20which%20has%20since%20invested%20in%20hundreds%20of%20early-stage%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBackend%20Capital%20raised%20%248%20million%20for%20its%20first%20fund%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20%2440%20million%20second%20fund.%20Some%20of%20her%20notable%20investments%20include%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Framp-raised-750-million-valuation-reaches-81-billion-di-coatue-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpense%20management%20platform%20Ramp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20compensation%20benchmarking%20tool%20Pave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20her%20venture%20fund%2C%20Guo%20cofounded%20the%20startup%20incubator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falcohol-free-san-francisco-house-hf0-ai-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHF0%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%20with%20Dave%20Fontenot%2C%20who%20continues%20to%20run%20the%20program.%20For%20the%20three-month%20program%2C%20founders%20live%20together%20in%20a%20large%20San%20Francisco%20mansion%2C%20focusing%20entirely%20on%20building%20their%20startups.%20In%20exchange%20for%205%25%20equity%20and%20a%20%241%20million%20uncapped%20investment%2C%20HF0%20takes%20care%20of%20%26quot%3Beverything%20that%20a%20founder%20spends%20time%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20food%2C%20laundry%2C%20and%20fitness%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20living%20with%20all%20these%20founders%2C%20I%20started%20getting%20the%20itch%20to%20build%20a%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Guo%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20that%20living%20with%20founders%20and%20essentially%20incubating%20companies%20or%20helping%20other%20companies%20would%20fulfill%20me%2C%20but%20I%20was%20just%20like%2C%20ugh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20growing%20desire%20to%20create%20something%20of%20her%20own%20again%20led%20Guo%20to%20a%20new%20idea%3A%20Passes%2C%20a%20creator-focused%20monetization%20platform%20that%20she%20founded%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCreators%20are%20entrepreneurs%2C%26quot%3B%20Guo%20said%2C%20citing%20examples%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-does-kylie-jenner-make-money-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKylie%20Jenner's%20lipsticks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjake-paul-controversies-timeline-looting-scandals-racist-slurs-drama-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJake%20Paul's%3C%2Fa%3E%20men's%20personal%20care%20brand.%20She%20believes%20that%20creators%20are%20key%20to%20marketing%20their%20products%20and%20should%20have%20better%20control%20over%20their%20audiences.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20thousand%20superfans%20that%20are%20willing%20to%20spend%20%245%20a%20day%20on%20you%2C%20that's%20an%20income.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuo's%20vision%20for%20Passes%20quickly%20gained%20traction.%20Guo%2C%20as%20the%20CEO%20and%20sole%20founder%2C%20raised%20a%20%249%20million%20seed%20round%20led%20by%20Multicoin%20Capital%20within%20a%20week%20of%20initiating%20the%20raise.%20%26quot%3BWe%20literally%20had%20no%20name