Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20alimony%20demand%2C%20reports%20also%20said%2C%20included%20Rs%204-5%20lakh%20for%20medical%20bill%2C%20which%20includes%20treatment%20and%20physiotherapy%20for%20knee%20pain%20that%20was%20attributed%20to%20the%20ex-husband's%20%26quot%3Bnegligence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20was%20unimpressed.%20According%20to%20legal%20news%20website%20Bar%20and%20Bench%2C%20Justice%20Kanneganti%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BDoes%20anybody%20spend%20this%20much%3F%20A%20single%20lady%20(by)%20herself...%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20did%20not%2C%20though%2C%20dismiss%20the%20demand%20for%20alimony%2C%20and%20called%20on%20the%20woman%20to%20present%20a%20more%20reasonable%20account%20of%20expenses.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20an%20order...%20I%20want%20actual%20figures%2C%20not%20this%20'lakhs%20of%20rupees'.%20Otherwise%20I%20will%20dismiss%20your%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Flet-her-earn-why-karnataka-hc-denied-rs-6-lakh%2Fmonth-alimony-to-woman%2Farticleshow%2F112715844.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20also%20warned%20against%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bexploit%20the%20process%20of%20the%20court%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20according%20to%20the%20above%20report%2C%20she%20was%20also%20ticked%20off%20for%20trying%20to%20bargain%20with%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20client%20is%20not%20understanding...%20you%20(her%20lawyer)%20should%20understand%20and%20advise%20her.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20place%20for%20bargaining.%20You%20are%20supposed%20to%20tell%20the%20court%20her%20actual%20expenses.%20We%20will%20give%20you%20one%20last%20chance%20to%20be%20reasonable...%20else%20straightaway%20we%20will%20dismiss%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20declared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%2