MZ)%20in%20Panmunjom%2C%202002.%20%5BONLY%20LICENSED%20FOR%20USE%20IN%20THIS%20ARTICLE%5D%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7694b1aa2ac29ee3361cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESouth%20Korean%20and%20US%20military%20personnel%20steps%20away%20from%20Simon%20on%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20Demilitarized%20Zone%20(DMZ)%20in%202002.%20He%20says%20they%20didn't%20say%20hello%20when%20greeted.%3Cp%3ESimon%20Cockerell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESimon%20Cockerell%2C%20a%20tour%20operator%2C%20has%20visited%20North%20Korea%20more%20than%20180%20times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENorth%20Korea%20is%20opening%20partially%20to%20tourism%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20visiting%20can%20be%20full%20of%20pitfalls%2C%20like%20mentioning%20religion%20or%20South%20Korea.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Simon%20Cockerell%2C%20a%20manager%20at%20the%20travel%20agency%20Koryo%20Tours.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20went%20to%20North%20Korea%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20knew%20what%20to%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20living%20in%20Beijing%20at%20the%20time%2C%20which%20was%20near%20North%20Korea.%20I%20figured%20it%20would%20be%20a%20bit%20like%20China%20or%20a%20bit%20like%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20definitely%20those%20elements%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20look%20for%20them%3B%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20it%20is%20its%20own%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20two%20decades%20since%20then%2C%20I've%20visited%20North%20Korea%20more%20than%20180%20times%20on%20various%20tours%20and%20trips%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20the%20most%20of%20any%20Westerner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tour%20operator%20Simon%20Cockerell%20on%20his%20first%20trip%20to%20North%20Korea%20in%202002.%20Pictured%20with%20a%20North%20Korean%20contact%20in%20front%20of%20a%20statue%20of%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Il%20Sung.%20%5BDO%20NOT%20USE%20IN%20ANY%20OTHER%20ARTICLES%2C%20ONLY%20LICENSED%20FOR%20USE%20IN%20THIS%20PIECE%5D%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7677743b5e59d16b45c57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22767%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETour%20operator%20Simon%20Cockerell%20on%20his%20first%20trip%20to%20North%20Korea%20in%202002.%20Pictured%20with%20a%20North%20Korean%20tour%20guide%20in%20front%20of%20a%20statue%20of%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Il%20Sung%20in%20Pyongyang.%3Cp%3ESimon%20Cockerell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea%20has%20been%20closed%20to%20visitors%20for%20almost%20five%20years%2C%20but%20is%20partially%20opening%20up%20to%20tourists%20at%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20shown%20hundreds%20of%20visitors%20around%20the%20country%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20if%20you've%20ever%20thought%20of%20visiting%2C%20this%20is%20how%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20a%20trip%20to%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22efe9a0a2-55aa-4ae3-9d41-98225c507598%5C%22%3ECareful%20what%20you%20talk%20about%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInteracting%20with%20the%20local%20people%20and%20tour%20guides%20in%20the%20country%20is%20not%20like%20meeting%20aliens%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20actually%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20things%20to%20do.%20The%20fact%20remains%20though%2C%20that%20when%20you're%20allowed%20to%20interact%20with%20them%2C%20you%20need%20to%20watch%20what%20you%20talk%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20around%20praising%20North%20Korea's%20leaders%2C%20but%20openly%20criticizing%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20is%20a%20definite%20no-no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20technically%20allowed%20to%20talk%20about%20what%20I%20want%20because%20I'm%20not%20a%20North%20Korean%2C%20but%20I%20am%20also%20aware%20that%20people%20there%20don't%20have%20that%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20I%20go%20over%20there%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20hey%20guys%2C%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20truth%20about%20your%20leaders%2C%20they're%20actually%20quite%20terrible%2C%26quot%3B%20I'm%20putting%20them%20in%20a%20very%2C%20very%20dangerous%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221338%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tour%20operator%20Simon%20Cockerell%20with%20Grammy-award%20winning%20singer%20Joss%20Stone%20on%20an%20unofficial%20trip%20to%20North%20Korea%20where%20she%20performed%20as%20part%20of%20her%20%26quot%3Bfull%20world%20tour%26quot%3B%20%5BONLY%20LICENSED%20FOR%20USE%20IN%20THIS%20ARTICLE%5D%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c76baa1aa2ac29ee3362ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESimon%20%5Bfar%20right%5D%20with%20Grammy-award%20winning%20singer%20Joss%20Stone%20%5Bcenter%5D%20and%20North%20Korean%20tour%20guides%20at%20Pyongyang%20Airport%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20tour.%3Cp%3ESimon%20Cockerell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETourism%20is%20important%20to%20some%20people%20there%2C%20but%20nothing%20is%20more%20important%20than%20the%20perception%20of%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20some%20common%20ground%20to%20talk%20about%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20work%20at%20it%20because%20your%20cultural%20references%20are%20all%20completely%20different.%20So%20you%20can't%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20gosh%2C%20did%20you%20see%20'Deadpool%20%26amp%3B%20Wolverine%3F'%26quot%3B%20because%20they%20will%20have%20no%20idea%20what%20you're%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ebcd089-28c6-43cd-b705-d2aa19fe3789%5C%22%3EAbsolutely%20no%20religious%20talk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20most%20common%20reason%20foreigners%20get%20detained%20in%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20ways%20