%20political%20risks%20as%20factors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20recommends%20defensive%20value%20stocks%20in%20healthcare%2C%20utilities%2C%20consumer%20staples%2C%20and%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20expect%20the%20stock%20market's%20seemingly%20unstoppable%20rally%20to%20continue%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20says%20Stifel's%20Barry%20Bannister.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20bank's%20chief%20US%20equity%20strategist%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20his%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20year-end%20target%20remains%205%2C000%2C%20around%2010%25%20below%20the%20market's%20closing%20level%20of%205%2C570%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20may%20sound%20unlikely%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20index's%2018%25%20returns%20year-to-date.%20But%20Bannister%20unpacked%20several%20risks%20facing%20the%20markets%20that%20he%20thinks%20investors%20are%20underappreciating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20investors%20have%20been%20anticipating%20rate%20cuts%20for%20months%20now%2C%20which%20has%20driven%20up%20market%20valuations.%20Market%20breadth%20has%20also%20been%20poor%2C%20by%20some%20measures%20%E2%80%94%20Bannister%20cited%20the%20Value%20Line%20Geometric%20Index%2C%20which%20tracks%20the%20market's%20mean%20stock%2C%20delivering%20barely-positive%20returns%20year-to-date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20both%20of%20these%20things%20set%20the%20market%20up%20for%20a%20pullback%20in%20either%20an%20inflationary%20or%20falling%20growth%20scenario%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20which%20is%20more%20likely%20by%20Bannister's%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Bannister%20believes%20there's%20an%20%26quot%3Binordinate%26quot%3B%20amount%20of%20political%20risk%20with%20the%20election%20approaching.%20Both%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20are%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20this%20will%20be%20the%20most%20consequential%20election%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20policy%20route%20the%20US%20takes%20since%201980.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Harris%20presidency%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Trump's%202017%20tax%20cuts%20would%20likely%20expire%2C%20meaning%20a%20broad%20tax%20hike%20from%20current%20levels.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Trump%20would%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20deliver%20a%20new%20tax-cut%20plan%20if%20he%20had%20support%20in%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20of%20those%20moments%20where%20the%20two%20visions%20are%20just%20absolutely%20diametrically%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeopolitical%20turmoil%20could%20also%20heat%20up%20further%20after%20the%20election%2C%20according%20to%20Bannister%2C%20because%20countries%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20face%20backlash%20during%20the%20lame%20duck%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Russia%20makes%20a%20countermove%20in%20Kursk%2C%20it%20would%20probably%20be%20between%20the%20election%20and%20January%2C%26quot%3B%20Bannister%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20Iran%20is%20likely%20to%20respond%20to%20some%20of%20the%20recent%20Israeli%20actions%20between%20the%20election%20and%20January.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20will%20also%20decide%20on%20stimulatory%20economic%20policy%20based%20on%20who%20wins%2C%20he%20said.%20For%20instance%2C%20it%20will%20be%20less%20likely%20to%20devalue%20its%20currency%20under%20a%20Trump%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bannister%20does%20not%20see%20a%20recession%20as%20his%20base-case%20scenario%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20one%20is%20there%2C%20and%20would%20mean%20even%20more%20downside%20for%20stocks%2C%20he%20said%20in%20an%20August%205%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20we%20describe%20a%20low%20double-digit%20correction%20there%20is%20also%20risk%20of%20a%20bear%20market%20if%20the%20slowdown%20becomes%20a%20recession%20which%2C%20by%20history%20and%20definition%2C%20would%20be%20a%20surprise%20to%20investors%20and%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22123e50c0-3ca9-4417-bae5-59f281faab21%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4%20trades%20to%20make%20amid%20market%20turbulence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20market%20poised%20for%20a%20turbulent%20period%20ahead%2C%20Bannister%20said%20he%20prefers%20defensive%20value%20stocks%2C%20particularly%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Ehealthcare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Eutilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Econsumer%20staples%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3Ereal%20estate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20sectors.%20Defensive%20stocks%2C%20which%20are%20those%20whose%20performance%20are%20not%20impacted%20by%20economic%20cycles%2C%20should%20get%20a%20boost%20from%20recession%20fears%2C%20and%20value%20stocks%2C%20which%20trade%20at%20a%20discount%2C%20benefit%20from%20lower%20inflation%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20important%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20these%20trades%2C%20he%20added%2C%20because%20much%20of%20the%20gains%20occur%20before%20the%20market%20or%20economic%20turmoil%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeventy%20percent%20of%20all%20the%20outperformance%20of%20defensive%20or%20value%20occurs%20before%20a%20recession%20is%20actually%20declared%2C%26quot%3B%20Bannister%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20while%20we're%20not%20calling%20for%20a%20recession%2C%20it%20pays%20to%20be%20preemptive%20with%20that%20group%20because%20they%20tend%20to%20outperform%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20nice%20place%20to%20be%20during%20a%20correction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExamples%20of%20funds%20that%20offer%20exposure%20to%20the%20above%20sectors%20include%20the%20Invesco%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20Equal%20Weight%20Health%20Care%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Finvesco-sp-500-equal-weight-health-care-etf-us46137v3327%3FmiRedirects%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERSPH%3C%2Fa%3E)%3B%20the%20Utilities%20Select%20Sector%20SPDR%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22htt