round%2010%20hours%2C%20in%20the%20second%20and%20final%20leg%20of%20his%20two-nation%20trip.%20He%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20National%20Security%20Adviser%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%9A%A1%20Indian%20PM%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20Kyiv%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Ukraine-India%20bilateral%20relations.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%93%B9%3A%20Ukrzaliznytsia%20%2F%20Instagram%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FN1lBzOy06P%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FN1lBzOy06P%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20UNITED24%20Media%20(%40United24media)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUnited24media%2Fstatus%2F1826873602349691172%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20will%20hold%20both%20one-on-one%20and%20delegation-level%20talks%20with%20Zelensky%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20ways%20to%20find%20a%20negotiated%20settlement%20to%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20visit%20by%20an%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20to%20Ukraine%20since%20the%20country%20became%20independent%20in%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20opportunity%20to%20build%20upon%20earlier%20conversations%20with%20President%20Zelenskyy%20on%20strengthening%20bilateral%20cooperation%20and%20share%20perspectives%20on%20peaceful%20resolution%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Ukraine%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20had%20said%20before%20leaving%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20so%20far%20maintained%20a%20neutral%20stance%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20calling%20for%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20to%20resolve%20the%20conflict.%20Modi's%20government%20has%20expanded%20India's%20non-alignment%20policy%20to%20%26quot%3Bmulti-alignment%2C%26quot%3B%20engaging%20with%2