20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20disgusted%20and%20suffocated.%20There%2C%20aspirants%20compromise%20on%20everything%20from%20rents%20to%20quality%20food.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20really%20do%20not%20need%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%20for%20preparation.%20This%20could%20have%20been%20true%20a%20few%20years%20back%20when%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20online%20resources%20and%20guidance.%20If%20you%20feel%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20atmosphere%20for%20studies%20at%20home%2C%20you%20can%20rent%20some%20property%20in%20a%20nearby%20town%20and%20join%20a%20library.%20While%20it%20is%20not%20important%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20have%20a%20mentor%20and%20a%20structured%20study%20routine%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Akash%2C%20who%20himself%20sought%20guidance%20from%20a%20retired%20DFO%20(Divisional%20Forest%20Officer)%20during%20his%20preparation%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat-based%20Akash%20had%20prepared%20for%20one%20of%20the%20challenging%20examinations%20of%20the%20country%20from%20the%20comforts%20of%20his%20home%20in%20a%20small%20village%20of%20Somnath%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20options%20of%20preparing%20for%20the%20exam%20by%20joining%20the%20coaching%20centres%20in%20Gandhinagar%20or%20Ahmedabad%20but%20I%20chose%20to%20remain%20in%20my%20village.%20I%20never%20felt%20left%20out.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20felt%20privileged.%20My%20mornings%20started%20with%20chirping%20birds%20and%20fresh%20air.%20Whenever%20I%20felt%20stressed%20out%2C%20I%20would%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akash%20(second%20from%20left)%20is%20g