g%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fattackers-armed-with-guns-and-rpgs-kill-11-police-officers-in-pakistan-ambush-13201225%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fattackers-armed-with-guns-and-rpgs-kill-11-police-officers-in-pakistan-ambush-13201225%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Words%20In%20Emails%2C%20Online%20Posts%20Lowering%20Woman's%20Dignity%20An%20Offence%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWritten%20words%2C%20either%20through%20email%20or%20on%20social%20media%2C%20that%20could%20lower%20the%20dignity%20of%20a%20woman%20constitutes%20an%20offence%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20said%20while%20refusing%20to%20quash%20a%20case%20against%20a%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20A%20S%20Gadkari%20and%20Neela%20Gokhale%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20a%20man%20seeking%20to%20quash%20the%202009%20case%20lodged%20against%20him%20under%20section%20509%20(insulting%20the%20modesty%20of%20a%20woman)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20had%20allegedly%20written%20offensive%20and%20insulting%20emails%20to%20the%20complainant%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20same%20south%20Mumbai%20society%20as%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emails%2C%20as%20per%20the%20complainant%2C%20made%20comments%20on%20her%20character%20and%20were%20forwarded%20to%20several%20other%20society%20members%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20sought%20quashing%20of%20the%20FIR%20contending%20that%2C%20as%20per%20section%20509%2C%20the%20word%20'uttered'%20would%20only%20mean%20'spoken%20words'%20and%20not%20words%20'written'%20in%20an%20email%20or%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20his%20arguments%20observing%20courts%20must%20adopt%20a%20purposive%20approach%20of%20interpretation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdvent%20of%20modern%20technology%20has%20opened%20up%20a%20wide%20spectrum%20of%20means%20to%20communicate%20an%20insult.%20When%20an%20e-mail%20containing%20objectionable%20content%20likely%20to%20outrage%20the%20modesty%20of%20a%20woman%20stares%20at%20her%2C%20can%20we%20permit%20the%20perpetrator%20to%20walk%20away%20undaunted%2C%20simply%20because%20the%20insult%20is%20written%20and%20not%20spoken%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterpretation%20must%20correspond%20to%20societal%20transformations%20and%20re-evaluate%20legal%20principles%20to%20ensure%20fairness%2C%20justice%20and%20equity%2C%20the%20HC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20society%20evolves%2C%20the%20interpretation%20of%20the%20law%20too%20must%20be%20evolved%20to%20address%20emerging%20challenges%20and%20promote%20social%20progress.%20The%20law%20is%20a%20dynamic%20entity%20capable%20of%20reflecting%20and%20adapting%20to%20a%20society's%20changing%20needs%20and%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20word%20'utterance'%20in%20the%20law%20must%20not%20be%20given%20a%20%26quot%3Bpedantic%20interpretation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20such%20a%20narrow%20interpretation%20is%20accepted%2C%20many%20men%20will%20walk%20away%2C%20unhindered%20by%20consequences%20merely%20by%20shooting%20emails%20or%20using%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20malign%20and%20insult%20a%20woman%20and%20outrage%20her%20modesty.%20Modern%20technology%20makes%20such%20manner%20of%20perpetrating%20the%20offence%20verily%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20emails%20are%20%26quot%3Bundeniably%20defamatory%20and%20aimed%20to%20lower%20the%20image%20and%20reputation%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20complainant%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20refused%20to%20quash%20the%20case.%20It%2C%20however%2C%20deleted%20the%20charges%20invoked%20against%20the%20man%20under%20IPC%20section%20354%20(assaults%20or%20uses%20criminal%20force%20to%20any%20woman%2C%20intending%20to%20outrag