3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKyani%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20iconic%20Parsi%20bakeries%20in%20Mumbai%20that%20serves%20authentic%20Parsi%20fare%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20LHS%3A%20Instagram%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fanecdotes_by_ruchee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERuchi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20RHS%3A%20Instagram%3A%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flets_comfort_it%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Food%20and%20Comfort%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20red%20checkered%20mats%20on%20the%20tables%20are%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20colonial%20setting%20in%20which%20the%20Parsi%20cafe%20scaled.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F321953%2Flist-of-eight-iconic-irani-cafes-in-mumbai-britannia-kyani-yazdani-ideal-corner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKyani%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20is%20a%20favourite%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20almost%20everyone%20who%20has%20walked%20through%20its%20rustic%20doors%2C%20and%20food%20writer%20Kalyan%20Karmarkar%20is%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20wriote%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ekheema%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20Kyani%20was%20indeed%20good.%20The%20meat%20and%20spices%20were%20robust%2C%20not%20smelly%20or%20too%20oily%20as%20it%20is%20in%20many%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20%3Cem%3Ekheema%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplaces.%20The%20%3Cem%3Eporo%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EParsi%3C%2Fem%3E-style%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eomelette)%20was%20pretty%20much%20the%20way%20my%20mom-in-law%20makes%20it%20and%20way%20tastier%20in%20this%20112-year-old%20place%20than%20omelettes%20(the%20far%20more%20expensive%20omelettes%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20new%20cafes).%20Though%20the%20smiles%20all%20around%20were%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%20breakfast.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Vig%20Refreshments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Edal%20pakwan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F134874%2Fsindhi-cuisine-traditional-recipes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESindhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20speciality%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20combines%20lentil%20curry%20with%20crispy%20fried%20bread)%20is%20a%20draw%20at%20this%2075-year-old%20eatery.%20Praveen%20whose%20great-grandfather%20was%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20the%20%3Cem%3Epakwan%20%3C%2Fem%3Erecipe%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EFaroma%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20following%20the%20Partition%2C%20the%20family%20moved%20from%20Lahore%20to%20Chembur%20in%20Mumbai%20where%20they%20settled%20in%20a%20refugee%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FavbTdyvoEyY%3Fsi%3DtazIr0DNjTwUKMmV%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20what%20makes%20the%20%3Cem%3Edal%20pakwan%3C%2Fem%3E%20phenomenal%2C%20Praveen%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNormally%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20%3Cem%3Echanne%20ka%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chickpea%20gravy)%20with%20sweet%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20added%20a%20twist%20with%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20ki%20sabzi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(potato%20vegetable)%2C%20%3Cem%3Emoong%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(curry%20made%20of%20green%20gram%20beans)%2C%20sweet%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ehara%20mirch%20%3C%2Fem%3E(green%20chilli)!%20It%20has%20a%20nice%20spicy%20kick%20now%3B%20a%20fusion%20of%20%3Cem%3ESindhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EPunjabi%3C%2Fem%3E%20cuisine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20other%20hits%20on%20the%20menu%20are%20%3Cem%3Echole%2