%20to%20grow%20a%20kilo%20of%20strawberries%20in%20vertical%20farming%2C%20farmers%20would%20only%20incur%20about%20Rs%20300%20to%20grow%20the%20same%20crop%20using%20AI%20enabled%20hydroponics%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Farish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Krop%20AI%20is%20building%20a%20farm%20setup%20for%20retail%20giants%20and%20integrating%20technology%20to%20grow%20the%20produce%20at%20affordable%20and%20a%20commercial%20scale.%20Their%20setup%2C%20Calvin%20says%2C%20costs%20Rs%205%20lakh%20and%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20grow%20500%20lettuce%20plants.%20So%20far%2C%20they%20have%20built%20farms%20for%20about%2010%20agri-entrepreneurs%20and%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Krop%20AI%20won%20the%20Karnataka%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Idea2POC%2FElevate%2F2023%20grant%20in%20the%20biotech%20sector.%20The%20startup%20is%20also%20incubated%20with%20the%20AIC%20Nitte%20incubation%20centre%20under%20the%20Startup%20India%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Calvin%20and%20Farish%20made%20a%20total%20revenue%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20with%20a%2040%20percent%20gross%20profit%20on%20manufacturing%20of%20farm%20stations.%20This%20year%2C%20they%20project%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20our%20technology%20allows%20us%20to%20grow%20crops%20indoors%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20perfect%20weather%20conditions%20for%20better%20harvests.%20Our%20plants%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357394%2Fhydroponics-farmers-increase-income-yield-reduce-water-wastage-india-saffron-strawberries-soil-less-farming-technique%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThis%2520method%2520of%2520farming%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520hydroponics%2Cstart%252C%2520we%2520have%2520you%2520covered.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20sun%20and%20soil%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20without%20compromising%20the%20taste.%20We%20are%20glad%20that%20within%20two%20years%20of%20time%2C%20we%20have%20not%20only%20been%20able%20to%20work%20on%20our%20patented%20technology%20but%20also%20revolutionised%20farming%20solutions%20for%20farmers.%20We%20hope%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20work%20and%20reach%20to%20small%20and%20medium%20income%20growers%20so%20that%20they%20can%20benefit%20from%20our%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Farish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Calvin%20Aranha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724062679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Calvin%20Aranha%20and%20Farish%20Anfal%2C%20from%20Udupi%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20started%20Krop%20AI.%20The%20hydroponics%20startup%20integrates%20technology%20and%20automation%20to%20enhance%20crop%20quality%20and%20production.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361688%2Fartificial-intelligence-ai-hydroponic-farming-grow-exotic-vegetables-farms-climate-change-krop-ai-udupi-startup%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RampMyCity%3A%20Paralysed%20After%20An%20Accident%2C%20Entrepreneur%20Makes%20Public%20Spaces%20Disabled-Friendly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrateek%20Khandelwal%E2%80%99s%20life%20took%20a%20major%20turn%20in%202014%20when%20he%20fell%20from%20an%20under-construction%20building.%20The%20accident%20left%20the%20IT%20engineer%20paralyzed%20from%20the%20waist%20below%20and%20in%20a%20wheelchair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Prateek%20was%20an%20energetic%20young%20professional%20with%20a%20successful%20career%20and%20an%20active%20social%20life%2C%20much%20like%20many%20others%20in%20their%20mid-20s.%20Today%2C%20he%20runs%20RampMyCity%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20works%20to%20improve%20accessibility%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%20and%20the%20elderly%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20adapted%20to%20his%20new%20reality%20back%20then%2C%20he%20knew%20that%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20let%20his%20wheelchair%20stop%20him%20from%20living%20fully.%20Although%20public%20attitudes%20towards%20him%20changed%2C%20with%20some%20friends%20offering%20him%20sympathy%20while%20others%20becoming%20distant%2C%20he%20committed%20himself%20to%20strenuous%20physical%20therapy%20during%20the%20first%20four%20years%20after%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfronted%20with%20complications%20such%20as%20bladder%20issues%20and%20muscle%20atrophy%20from%20his%20spinal%20cord%20injury%2C%20Prateek%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20his%20progress%20over%20dwelling%20on%20the%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20of%20physical%20training%20helped%20Prateek%20make%20significant%20progress%2C%20but%20he%20faced%20a%20new%20problem%3A%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20out%20to%20eat%20at%20his%20favourite%20restaurants%20or%20any%20other%20places%20he%20enjoyed%20before.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20create%20his%20startup%20as%20he%20understood%20just%20how%20crucial%20ramps%20were%20in%20breaking%20barriers%20and%20accessing%20the%20world%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202020%2C%20RampMyCity%20aims%20to%20provide%20complete%20infrastructure%20solutions%20for%20both%20public%20and%20private%20sectors.%20This%20includes%20ramps%2C%20accessibility%20audits%2C%20retrofitting%2C%20and%20more.%20So%20far%2C%20Prateek%20has%20helped%20install%20over%20530%20ramps%20in%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Goa%2C%20Gurgaon%2C%20and%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-27_11zon-1723818970.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22So%20far%2C%20Prateek%20has%20helped%20install%20over%20530%20ramps%20in%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Goa%2C%20Gurgaon%2C%20and%20Mumbai.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-27_11zon-1723818970.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-27_11zon-1723818970-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-27_11zon-1723818970-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-27_11zon-1723818970-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-27_11zon-1723818970-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361766%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESo%20far%2C%20Prateek%20has%20helped%20install%20over%20530%20ramps%20in%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Goa%2C%20Gurgaon%2C%20and%20Mumbai.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%20should%20I%20stop%20living%20my%20life%20when%20my%20mind%20and%20spirit%20are%20free%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrateek%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Nirbhik%20recalls%20that%20during%20his%20treatment%2C%20his%20chances%20of%20survival%20were%20slim.%20However%2C%20Prateek%20vowed%20to%20his%20doctor%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20come%20to%20you%20after%20two%20years%20and%20show%20you%20that%20my%20life%20does%20not%20end%20here.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20promise%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20Prateek%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20recovery.%20Initially%2C%20he%20saw%20his%20friends%20drifting%20away%20and%20a%20serious%20relationship%20coming%20to%20an%20end.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20his%20social%20life%20disappear%20and%20his%20situation%20worsen%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Nirbhik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20training%20under%20his%20physiotherapist%20for%208-10%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20Prateek%20carefully%20monitored%20how%20his%20bladder%20and%20stomach%20reacted%20to%20every%20bite%20of%20food%20and%20sip%20of%20liquid.%20%E2%80%9CRecovery%20involved%20a%20lot%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20improvement%20comes%20slowly%2C%20but%20persistence%20is%20key%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202017%2C%20he%20could%20stand%20with%20a%20walker%20and%20perform%20tasks%20like%20cooking%2C%20and%20even%20use%20crutches.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20he%20wondered%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20I%20stop%20living%20my%20life%20when%20my%20mind%20and%20spirit%20are%20free%20despite%20my%20challenges%3F%20I%20am%20ambitious%2C%20a%20big-time%20foodie%2C%20and%20love%20meeting%20my%20friends.%20Why%20should%20a%20wheelchair%20put%20an%20end%20to%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20not%20to%20let%20his%20wheelchair%20limit%20him%2C%20he%20began%20reaching%20out%20to%20his%20friends%20after%20four%20years%20of%20isolation.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20they%20were%20initially%20unsure%2C%20they%20eventually%20realised%20I%20was%20still%20the%20same%20person%20and%20invited%20me%20back%20into%20their%20social%20circles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20family%20struggled%20to%20find%20accessible%20locations%20for%20Prateek%2C%20so%20they%20took%20it%20upon%20themselves%20to%20install%20ramps.%20This%20way%2C%20he%20could%20join%20them%20in%20their%20outings%20to%20restaurants%20and%20theatres.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20to%20start%20a%20big%20business%20but%20to%20improve%20accessibility%20for%20people%20like%20Prateek%2C%20helping%20them%20enjoy%20a%20life%20similar%20to%20anyone%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nirbhik%2C%20adding%20that%20being%20able%20to%20go%20out%20for%20weekends%20and%20date%20nights%20boosted%20Prateek%E2%80%99s%20confidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiving%20him%20a%20normal%20life%20was%20the%20biggest%20success%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20effort%20to%20reconnect%20with%20the%20community%2C%20Prateek%20faced%20a%20harsh%20reality%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360927%2Fsweta-mantrii-comedian-spina-bifida-disability-stand-up-comedy-wheelchair-accessibility-inclusion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lack%20of%20accessibility%20in%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Despite%20living%20in%20a%20prestigious%20building%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20neither%20the%20building%20itself%20nor%20public%20spaces%20like%20banks%2C%20restaurants%2C%20metro%20or%20police%20stations%2C%20theatres%20were%20accessible%20to%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20realisation%20hit%20me%20hard%2C%20making%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20I%20were%20in%20a%20permanent%20lockdown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20with%20disabilities%20are%20forced%20to%20stay%20indoors%20because%20of%20such%20infrastructural%20barriers.%20The%20World%20Bank%20reports%20that%20about%2015%25%20of%20the%20global%20population%20has%20some%20form%20of%20disability.%20Given%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20of%20over%201.4%20billion%2C%20this%20translates%20to%20approximately%2021%20crore%20people%20with%20disabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20the%20question%3A%20Where%20are%20these%20individuals%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disabled%20community%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20often%20unseen%20and%20confined%20to%20their%20homes.%20An%20important%20question%20to%20consider%20then%20is%20what%20the%20government%20is%20doing%20about%20accessibility.%20The%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(RPwD)%20Act%20of%202016%20mandates%20equal%20access%20and%20universal%20design%20standards%2C%20but%20enforcement%20is%20often%20inadequate%20in%20the%20country.%3