20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361807%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVishnupriya%2C%20Barnala%20Michael%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20friends%20came%20together%20to%20solve%20the%20social%20issue%20through%20collective%20effort.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20community%2C%20for%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20began%20when%20Vishnupriya%20came%20across%20a%20heartbreaking%20news%20report%20about%20a%20young%20girl%20who%20tragically%20lost%20her%20life%20due%20to%20health%20complications%20from%20constipation%2C%20caused%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20toilets%20in%20her%20school.%20This%20disturbing%20incident%20propelled%20her%20into%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20already%20been%20working%20on%20a%20documentary%20%E2%80%98Meel%E2%80%99%20to%20show%20solutions%20for%20waste%20management%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20years.%20So%20she%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20constructing%20low-cost%20eco-friendly%20toilets%20for%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Nellivasal%20village.%20After%20initial%20discussions%20with%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20people%20and%20friends%2C%20they%20approached%20Michael%20to%20devise%20a%20plan%20to%20solve%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20us%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20project%20come%20from%20areas%20of%20water%20scarcity.%20We%20have%20known%20the%20issues%20of%20toilet%20facilities%20and%20the%20pain%20of%20open%20defecation.%20This%20problem%20aggravates%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%20This%20was%20a%20common%20emotional%20pain%20point%2C%20which%20motivated%20us%20to%20come%20together%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Michael.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dire%20situation%20where%20children%20were%20forced%20to%20defecate%20in%20the%20open%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20facilities%2C%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20