https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20at%20the%20school%20campus.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20sought%20permission%20from%20the%20forest%20department%20to%20construct%20low-cost%20and%20sustainable%20toilets%20for%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20given%20a%20month%E2%80%99s%20time.%20We%20found%20that%20mobilising%20construction%20materials%20and%20workers%20was%20difficult%20in%20the%20area.%20So%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20be%20smart%20in%20building%20toilets%20which%20will%20require%20less%20cost%2C%20time%2C%20and%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20project%20was%20entirely%20funded%20by%20volunteers%20of%20the%20Cuckoo%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20design%2C%20cost%2C%20technique%3A%20constructing%20unique%20toilets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20preparing%20a%20rough%20design%20for%20toilets%20in%20October%202023%2C%20Michael%20and%20the%20team%20started%20constructing%20the%20toilets.%20They%20employed%20innovative%20construction%20techniques%2C%20opting%20for%20ferrocement%20structures%20to%20reduce%20costs%20and%20expedite%20the%20building%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFerrocement%20construction%20technique%20is%20a%20low-cost%20method%20that%20is%20less%20labour%20intensive.%20In%20this%2C%20reinforced%20cement%20is%20applied%20over%20a%20chicken%20metal%20mesh.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20used%20polycarbonate%20sheet%2C%20a%20translucent%20material%20that%20allows%20natural%20light%20and%20outside%20visibility%20that%20could%20enable%20students%20to%20feel%20slight%20resemblance%20with%20their%20old%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20also%20used%20a%20leech%20pit%20system%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F78181%2Fvideo-waterless-toilets-just-rural-india-needs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEco%2520sans%2520toilet%2520costs%2520about%2C%2527flush%2520out%2527%2520the%2520waste.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20human%20waste%20into%20natural%20manure%20for%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20system%2C%20two%20pits%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20toilet%20and%20they%20are%20built%20such%20that%20water%20gets%20drained%20through%20its%20walls%20and%20solid%20waste%20remains%20in%20the%20pit.%20When%20one%20pit%20gets%20filled%2C%20excreta%20is%20collected%20in%20the%20next%20pit.%20Meanwhile%2C%20solid%20waste%20in%20the%20former%20turns%20into%20manure%20in%20that%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20construction%20of%20toilets%20has%20been%20extremely%20convenient%20for%20school%20children%2C%20especially%20hostellers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20construction%20of%20toilets%20has%20been%20extremely%20convenient%20for%20school%20children%2C%20especially%20hostellers.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWater%20is%20the%20main%20medium%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20microbes.%20When%20you%20remove%20water%20from%20solid%20waste%2C%20it%20does%20not%20cause%20any%20bad%20smell.%20Pits%20that%20have%20porous%20walls%20permit%20the%20contents%20to%20seep%20into%20the%20ground.%20Sawdust%20is%20applied%20to%20arrest%20the%20bad%20smell%20and%20microbial%20growth.%20It%20is%20a%20sustainable%20and%20natural%20way%20of%20waste%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Michael%20says%20they%20have%20designed%20the%20toilets%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20draws%20the%20interest%20of%20students%20who%20were%20accustomed%20to%20open%20defecation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20built%20toilets%20in%20oval%20round%20shapes%20and%20adorned%20with%20vibrant%20colours%20to%20attract%20the%20students%20to%20use%20the%20enclosed%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F102470%2Fcarambolim-goa-village-eco-friendly-toilets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20approach%20%3C%2Fa%3Enot%20only%20addressed%20hygiene%20concerns%20but%20also%20promoted%20sustainable%20practices%20within%20the%20community.%20The%20project%20was%20completed%20by%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20their%20work%20was%20immediate%20and%20profound.%20The%20newly%20constructed%20toilets%20not%20only%20provided%20essential%20facilities%20but%20also%20triggered%20a%20behavioural%20change%20among%20the%20students.%20Built%20mainly%20for%20the%20boys%E2%80%99%20hostel%20at%20the%20campus%2C%20currently%20about%2080%20rural%20students%20including%20boys%20and%20g