ecessary%20speed%20for%20a%20100-metre%20lap%20during%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20was%20holding%20her%20back%20%E2%80%94%20her%20father%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20given%20her%20his%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKiran%20Chavan%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20his%20daughter%20wanted%20to%20put%20herself%20through%20such%20a%20demanding%20ordeal.%20He%20was%20apprehensive%2C%20knowing%20of%20people%20who%20had%20lost%20their%20lives%20attempting%20this%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20her%20to%20put%20herself%20in%20a%20life-threatening%20position.%20She%20was%20doing%20well%20in%20her%20business%2C%20as%20a%20mother%20and%20wife.%20Why%20put%20your%20life%20at%20risk%3F%20I%20wanted%20to%20protect%20my%20daughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kiran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Tanvi%20was%20determined%20and%20persuasive.%20When%20letters%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20she%20asked%20her%20coach%20to%20convince%20her%20father.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20her%20coach%20met%20me%20and%20assured%20me%20that%20there%20was%20no%20risk%20of%20life%20and%20she%20would%20be%20taken%20care%20of%2C%20it%20convinced%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMagically%2C%20Tanvi%20was%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20required%20timing%20the%20next%20day%20and%20since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20She%20slowly%20gained%20her%20confidence%20back%20and%20started%20practice%20in%20earnest%20for%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20big%20challenge%20to%20tackle%20was%20the%20cold%20conditions%20of%20the%20English%20Channel.%20To%20get%20acclimatised%20to%20cold%20water%2C%20Tanvi%20first%20started%20taking%20only%20cold%20showers.%20She%20also%20started%20sitting%20in%20ice%20baths%20for%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20which%20later%20increased%20to%20one%20hour.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20sit%20in%20ice%20water%20from%202%20am%20to%203%20am%20to%20get%20used%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanvi%20found%20happiness%20in%20swimming%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361699%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanvi%20found%20happiness%20in%20swimming.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20practised%20in%20Nainital%E2%80%99s%20Naini%20lake%20for%20a%20week%2C%20which%20has%20conditions%20similar%20to%20the%20English%20Channel.%20Unfortunately%2C%20when%20she%20reached%20Nainital%2C%20it%20snowed%2C%20which%20made%20the%20water%20extremely%20cold.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20coach%20motivated%20me%20to%20swim.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98This%20is%20it%E2%80%99.%20I%20swam%20in%2011%20degrees%20Celsius%20water%20temperature%2C%20which%20helped%20my%20body%20get%20used%20to%20such%20cold%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManaging%20time%20became%20a%20significant%20challenge%20for%20Tanvi.%20She%20would%20practice%20in%20the%20morning%20from%204%20am%20to%207%20am%2C%20send%20the%20kids%20off%20to%20school%2C%20go%20to%20the%20office%2C%20and%20then%20practice%20again%20in%20the%2