0being%20%E2%80%9Cfussy%E2%80%9D%20about%20her%20food%20preferences%2C%20luxuries%20and%20comforts.%20Bad%20weather%20would%20tick%20her%20off.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20time%20she%20spent%20on%20the%20road%2C%20where%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359311%2Fchavni-maratha-camp-lohagad-visapur-fort-pune-maharashtra-heritage-stay-hotel-sustainable-tents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadapt%20to%20the%20local%20diaspora%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20she%20truly%20discovered%20herself%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20discovered%20my%20father%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98I%20came%20to%20respect%20his%20love%20for%20riding%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20trip%20to%20Nandi%20Hills%20in%20school%20days%2C%20Angelica%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20trip%20where%20I%20observed%20how%20seriously%20my%20dad%20took%20motorbike%20riding%2C%20learnt%20the%20proper%20way%20of%20sitting%20on%20the%20bike%20and%20holding%20when%20hairpin%20bends%20approached.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20short%20trips%20taught%20her%20the%20nuances%20of%20becoming%20a%20good%20pillion.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20helping%20my%20dad%20by%20spotting%20traffic%20coming%20from%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20curve%20and%20watching%20out%20for%20road%20crossings.%20These%20things%20helped%20my%20dad%20focus%20on%20the%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98I%20understood%20his%20way%20of%20thinking%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357087%2Fmotorcycle-biking-trips-from-karnataka-to-kashmir-indian-bikers-tejas-g-r-shares-safety-tips-planning%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEvery%20trip%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20ups%20and%20downs.%20Ajay%20and%20Angelica%20were%20no%20s