y%20about%20my%20safety%3B%20whether%20taking%20me%20along%20was%20the%20right%20decision%3B%20would%20I%20be%20okay%20being%20so%20far%20away%20from%20home%3B%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20something%20were%20to%20go%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20was%20only%20when%20we%20started%20travelling%20that%20he%20started%20seeing%20me%20as%20his%20morale%20booster%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Whenever%20the%20duo%20would%20hit%20a%20roadblock%2C%20Angelica%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20hear%20of%20turning%20back.%20The%20only%20way%20was%20forward%2C%20she%E2%80%99d%20say.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20began%20to%20see%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20a%20child%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98I%20taught%20him%20some%20things%20too%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Arts%20student%2C%20Angelica%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347041%2Fkochi-heritage-project-by-johann-kuruvilla-documenting-art-culture-heritage-walks-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20for%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20significant%20roads%2C%20and%20historic%20spots%20were%20known%20to%20Ajay.%20But%20it%20was%20only%20when%20she%20was%20briefing%20him%20about%20these%20while%20standing%20at%20the%20spot%20in%20question%20that%20he%20understood%20how%20well-versed%20his%20daughter%20was%20in%20these%20topics.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5Bmy%20father%5D%20would%20listen%20patiently%20and%20then%20proceed%20to%20compliment%20me%20that%20I%E2%80%99d%20been%20paying%20attention%20at%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Angelica.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftravel-2-1723198283.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20motorbike%20expeditions%20have%20been%20a%20great%20bo